oup埋學結他😅"},{"pid":"7337d099acf9f05715bfe9b4115c4418b5c041a9","tid":163540,"uid":70249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:32:59.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"df730c33339c0655900f3e38a8b2c4bc9ecadae7","tid":163540,"uid":70249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:11:04.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"4127cf6050fe57929cfe7471426e57bbe9853738","tid":163540,"uid":16156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:36:23.000Z","msg":"Jazz同blue都叫小眾，咁我地classical算咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n級數唔洗睇得太重要，8級只係3首歌，談唔上叫識，就算比你FTCL,都係果句，上台彈啦,對人彈咪見真章<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f010cbfa5676cf3cbd5f1a01737d1cca19bd58c","tid":163540,"uid":70249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:20:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Jazz同blue都叫小眾，咁我地classical算咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n級數唔洗睇得太重要，8級只係3首歌，談唔上叫識，就算比你FTCL,都係果句，上台彈啦,對人彈咪見真章<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反而覺得Cassical多人識少少，因為考級個啲一定要學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話8級唔重要、對人表演見真章呢個真係完全同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過以前屋企人又唔太識野，自己又話鍾意就走去學，不過學到6級就發現自己學緊嘅音樂根本就唔係我想學嘅音樂，所以考咗8級都無再考上去。而家跟呢個阿Sir學得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPs. 其實有啲古典都幾好聽，我都鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1adfd74560e4f0a28ceefd528ac6a458021659","tid":163540,"uid":70249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T07:34:35.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"5379768d609393aff11908a1daccec6d85955192","tid":163540,"uid":70249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:29:37.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"f520b98cc7e1117f0b76414958216fd902f34838","tid":163540,"uid":70249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:21:33.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"593eb0e236735513d887c9b9f831781383094747","tid":163540,"uid":31632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}